1145	/// rule's `openProtoRule` yields a non-empty AC list.  See
1146	/// [`rule_open_ac_nonempty`].  When True the theory renders via the
1147	/// open-as-closed path, which suppresses loop-breaker comments on
1148	/// trivial-AC-variant rules whose AC form equals their E form.
1149	fn contains_manual_rule_variants(
1150	    parsed: &p::Theory,
1151	    elaborated: &Theory,
